'''杰里米·布洛奇'''（{{Lang-en|Jeremy Bulloch}}，{{bd|1945年|2月16日|2020年|12月17日|catIdx=Bulloch}}）是[[英国|英国]]一名[[演员|演员]]。他因在电影《[[星球大战V：帝国反击战|星球大战V：帝国反击战]]》和《[[星球大战VI：绝地归来|星球大战VI：绝地归来]]》中饰演[[波巴·费特|波巴·费特]]而享誉国际，同时他也出演过许多英国电视剧，如《[[神秘博士|神秘博士]]》和《{{Link-en|舍伍德的罗宾|Robin of Sherwood}}》等。2020年12月17日，罹患[[帕金森病|帕金森病]]多年的杰里米·布洛奇病逝于[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[圣乔治医院|圣乔治医院]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Star Wars' Boba Fett actor Jeremy Bulloch dies aged 75 |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-55358301 |publisher=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]] |accessdate=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2020-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217235610/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-55358301 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Peter Sblendorio |title=‘Star Wars’ actor Jeremy Bulloch, who played Boba Fett, dead at 75 |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/snyde/ny-star-wars-actor-jeremy-bulloch-boba-fett-20201217-73fx57jvxjgqtnzumd4luwfvea-story.html |publisher=[[纽约日报|纽约日报]] |accessdate=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116142051/https://www.nydailynews.com/snyde/ny-star-wars-actor-jeremy-bulloch-boba-fett-20201217-73fx57jvxjgqtnzumd4luwfvea-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Diana Dasrath |author2=David K. Li |author3=Doha Madani |title=Jeremy Bulloch, Boba Fett actor in original 'Star Wars' trilogy, dies at 75 |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/jeremy-bulloch-boba-fett-original-star-wars-trilogy-dies-75-n1251620 |publisher=[[NBC新闻|NBC新闻]] |accessdate=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218025249/https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/jeremy-bulloch-boba-fett-original-star-wars-trilogy-dies-75-n1251620 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Jeremy Bulloch, Original Boba Fett Actor in ‘Star Wars’ Films, Dies at 75 |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/jeremy-bulloch-dead-boba-fett-star-wars-1234865498/ |publisher=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] |accessdate=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2021-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302070109/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/jeremy-bulloch-dead-boba-fett-star-wars-1234865498/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 早年经历 ==
杰里米·布洛奇出生于[[英国|英国]][[莱斯特郡|莱斯特郡]]的[[马基特哈伯勒|马基特哈伯勒]]，是家里的六个孩子之一。在布洛奇5岁时，他在一次学校表演之后喜欢上了表演和唱歌。他从10岁的时候开始参与演出，并“出现在几部[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]电影，以及英国[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]和戏剧里”<ref>{{cite book |author1=J. W. Rinzler |coauthors=Ridley Scott |title=The Making of Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back |date=2013-10-22 |publisher=Ballantine Group |location=[[伦敦|伦敦]] |isbn=9780345543363 |page=132 |edition=Enhanced Edition |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-U0PAAAAQBAJ&q=the+making+of+the+empire+strikes+back#v=snippet&q=the%20making%20of%20the%20empire%20strikes%20back&f=false |accessdate=2020-12-19}}</ref>。他曾在{{Link-en|科罗纳戏剧学校|Corona Theatre School|科罗纳舞台学院}}接受训练<ref>{{cite web |title=Sally Bulloch |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1896195/Sally-Bulloch.html |publisher=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |accessdate=2020-12-20 |quote=After attending the Corona stage school, where her brother Jeremy was also a pupil |archive-date=2019-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223200411/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1896195/Sally-Bulloch.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{Sfnp|McFarlane|2006|p=99}}。

